author: IGN
description:
What happens when a game developer watches their work get absolutely broken by a speedrunner? In this video, Blue Prince creator Tonda Ros sits down with IGN to react to a full Bequest% speedrun by speedrunner Taiwon. From clever exploits to unexpected skips, see how a speedrunner pushes the game to its limits and hear the dev’s live commentary on what’s intentional, what’s surprising, and what’s downright wild!

#BluePrince #Gaming #IGN
title: Blue Prince Developer Reacts to 11 Minute Speedrun

author: IGN
description:
Take a look at the Exclusive Announcement Trailer for Project Retrograde, a narrative-driven action survival game developed by Invercity Games Works. Players will make use of the game's Gungfu-centric combat system to explore, scavenge, and survive at all costs. Embody a bounty hunter to explore ancient ruins to uncover the cause of the apocalypse in Project Retrograde, coming soon to PlayStation 5 (PS5), Xbox, and PC (Steam).
